{"tid":42194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（1.9億）當年識攞，一定係攞玉璽","createTime":"2016-12-16T13:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T14:02:39.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc1e0e744281430cab3f9bb678fc275814930c7e","tid":42194,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"神秘中國買家 $1.7億奪乾隆玉璽<br />\n<br />\n【晴報專訊】一枚18世紀的清朝乾隆皇帝的玉璽，在本月14日的法國巴黎德魯奧拍賣會，由一匿名中國買家以2,100萬歐元（1.7億港元）投得，較原先估價高出超過20倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jn7037z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJn7037z.jpg&h=8efac2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壽山石雕刻9龍造型<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該玉璽由福建壽山石雕刻而成，紅白相間，上面雕刻9龍造型，象徵中國皇帝無上的權力。拍賣行指，在19世紀末，一位年輕的法國海軍醫生在中國得到了這件玉璽，並一直保存在這個家族的手中。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線，咁就發撚左，乜唔係要無條件歸還咩"},{"pid":"086314a4df53e131e450a49ea4d2cb173dac6eca","tid":42194,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"要有証明係搶返來先要交還"},{"pid":"3ce5166d75091ef7f0546a6f8d573980c662f14c","tid":42194,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fcf2adf080ce44fd9efdfdcdacea057976d5f44","tid":42194,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"如果有錢都想拍返舊過下皇帝癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f46755fd5df611b2386e566ea6b08100914dd38","tid":42194,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有錢都想拍返舊過下皇帝癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界的確大把人袁術心"},{"pid":"9c59ea1243ac03828431087888af368be7193354","tid":42194,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"洗白白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2350d230965ab66b596bc36be91e91fee555d8e","tid":42194,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"最正應該係十二生肖噴水鳩頭<br />\n如果儲得晒成套真係fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0686882fd1bc16a3f37ca6cebc9959f39894f8ab","tid":42194,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"得，還俾個姓愛新覺羅"}]}